mario <- read_delim("../dados/marioKart.txt", delim = "\t", col_types = "diicdddcicic") %>% 
  mutate(stockPhoto = ifelse(stockPhoto == "yes", TRUE, FALSE))
mario <- filter(mario, totalPr < 100)
names(mario)
 [1] "ID"         "duration"   "nBids"      "cond"       "startPr"    "shipPr"     "totalPr"   
 [8] "shipSp"     "sellerRate" "stockPhoto" "wheels"     "title"     
mario %>% 
  select(-title, -wheels) %>% 
  ggpairs(progress = FALSE)

mlm <- lm(totalPr ~ cond + startPr, data = mario)
tidy(mlm)
model_plot = mario %>% 
  data_grid(cond, startPr) %>% 
  add_predictions(mlm)
model_plot %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x  = startPr, colour = cond)) + 
  geom_line(aes(y = pred)) + 
  facet_grid(. ~ cond)

model_plot %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x  = startPr, colour = cond)) + 
  geom_line(aes(y = pred)) + 
  geom_point(data = mario, aes(y = totalPr)) + 
  facet_grid(. ~ cond)

tidy(mlm, conf.int = T)
glance(mlm)
